Canon to Invest $1 Billion on Two Plants in Taiwan, Economic Daily Reports

-- B y   A d e l a   L i n
-- 
2011-06-06T00:17:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-06/canon-to-invest-1-billion-on-two-plants-in-taiwan-economic-daily-reports.html
Canon Group plans to invest NT$30
billion to build two plants in  Taiwan , the Taipei-based Economic
Daily News reported, without saying where it got the
information. The Japanese group began construction of a plant to
make digital cameras in Taichung, central Taiwan, yesterday, the
newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Adela Lin in Taipei at 
 alin95@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Tim Smith at 
 tsmith58@bloomberg.net  